title: Google\Cloud\Compute\V1\Project
name: Project
description:
Represents a Project resource. A project is used to organize resources in a Google Cloud Platform environment. For more information, read about the Resource Hierarchy.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.compute.v1.Project

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

methods.description: Constructor.

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.common_instance_metadata
params.description: Metadata key/value pairs available to all instances contained in this project. See Custom metadata for more information.

params.name: data.creation_timestamp
params.description: [Output Only] Creation timestamp in RFC3339 text format.

params.name: data.default_network_tier
params.description: This signifies the default network tier used for configuring resources of the project and can only take the following values: PREMIUM, STANDARD. Initially the default network tier is PREMIUM. Check the DefaultNetworkTier enum for the list of possible values.

params.name: data.default_service_account
params.description: [Output Only] Default service account used by VMs running in this project.

params.name: data.description
params.description: An optional textual description of the resource.

params.name: data.enabled_features
params.description: Restricted features enabled for use on this project.

params.name: data.id
params.description: [Output Only] The unique identifier for the resource. This identifier is defined by the server. This is not the project ID, and is just a unique ID used by Compute Engine to identify resources.

params.name: data.kind
params.description: [Output Only] Type of the resource. Always compute#project for projects.

params.name: data.name
params.description: The project ID. For example: my-example-project. Use the project ID to make requests to Compute Engine.

params.name: data.quotas
params.description: [Output Only] Quotas assigned to this project.

params.name: data.self_link
params.description: [Output Only] Server-defined URL for the resource.

params.name: data.usage_export_location
params.description: The naming prefix for daily usage reports and the Google Cloud Storage bucket where they are stored.

params.name: data.xpn_project_status
params.description: [Output Only] The role this project has in a shared VPC configuration. Currently, only projects with the host role, which is specified by the value HOST, are differentiated. Check the XpnProjectStatus enum for the list of possible values.
